Description: ### About> Now it is even easier to use the rich and diverse collection of real-world concepts in OpenCyc to bring meaning to your semantic web applications! The full OpenCyc content is now available both as downloadable OWL ontologies as well as via semantic web endpoints (i.e.- permanent URIs). These URIs return RDF representations of each Cyc concept as well as a human-readable version when accessed via a Web Browser.Data exposed: OpenCyc OntologySize of dump and data set: ~1.6 million triples- ~150MB uncompressed### Openness[License](http://www.opencyc.org/license) states:> These files contain an OWL representation of information contained in the OpenCyc Knowledge Base.
